# --- (m) kw_dict on LIST<BLOB>      expression source ----------------------
# --- (n) kw_dict on ARRAY<BLOB>     expression source ----------------------
# --- (q) ng_dict on LIST<BLOB>      expression source ----------------------
# --- (r) ng_dict on ARRAY<BLOB>     expression source ----------------------
# --- (u) any_text_dict on LIST<BLOB>  expression source --------------------
